%% Diagram: Strict CSP nonce + 'strict-dynamic' lifecycle
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Client as Browser
    participant Edge as Edge / origin
    participant App as Application
    participant Loader as Trusted loader script

    Client->>Edge: GET /page
    Edge->>App: forward
    App->>App: nonce = randomBytes(16).base64
    App-->>Edge: HTML + Content-Security-Policy: script-src 'nonce-XYZ' 'strict-dynamic'
    Edge-->>Client: response with header + nonce on every legitimate <script>

    Client->>Client: parser sees inline <script nonce="XYZ"> -> allowed
    Client->>Loader: execute trusted bootstrap
    Loader->>Client: dynamically inject app bundles
    Note over Client,Loader: 'strict-dynamic' propagates trust<br/>to scripts created by trusted scripts

    Client-xClient: injected <script> without nonce -> blocked, CSP report sent
    Client->>Edge: POST /csp-report (report-to / report-uri)
